CONCRETE MIXING & CONVEYING CO., Plaintiff Appellee, v. ULEN CONTRACTING CORPORATION and Shandaken Tunnel Corporation, Defendants Appellants. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 3, 1926.) No. 332. James L. Steuart, of New York City, for appellants. Stephen J. Cox, of New York City, and Williams, Bradbury, McCaleb & Hinkle, of Chicago, Ill., for appellee.

Before ROGERS, HOUGH, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree (12 F.[2d] 929) affirmed.
